description: xDelica has a simple mission: To serve the most delicious dumplings. We use only the best ingredients -- Our meat is always all-natural and from the finest cuts. We serve beef, pork, chicken as well as vegan options. xDelica offers both authentic Asian classical (Chinese, Korean, Japanese, and Tibetan/Nepal momo) as well as bold fusions inspired by A2's creativity.Welcome to xDelica, we serve only the best dumplings.
name: Xdelica
